## Academic Use Notice

This project was developed for educational purposes as a college project. 
While the MIT License allows for commercial use, please note that this system 
was designed and implemented for academic evaluation and demonstration of 
web development skills, database design, and system architecture knowledge.

## Educational Purpose Statement

This Smart Inventory System is intended for:
- Academic evaluation and assessment
- Learning and educational purposes
- Demonstration of technical skills
- Portfolio and resume enhancement
- Educational research and study

